{"tid":1700210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1111應該重新定性，唔係［大罷工］，係大型［不合作運動］","createTime":"2019-11-08T11:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T09:59:09.000Z","uid":94771,"like":141,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"57cd75c2d7e7a610f815ac8e9e0bd106ab742c24","tid":1700210,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>現實層面來睇，大罷工係絕對無可能做到。<br />\n因為不論時間定文宣，都跟唔上</strong><br />\n<br />\n工會重味成功成立，只會做成小部份人罷工，佢地將比人秋後，白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n結果就係真正組織罷工個時，<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">會嚴重影響由工會＋大量文宣組織三罷的公信力</span></strong>（狼來了效應），最嚴重係會令工會難以組織。<br />\n<br />\n但咁係唔係咩都唔做，唔比１１１１行動，個人認為絕對唔係。只不過就唔好叫大罷工啦，應該叫大型不合作運動，性質係之前塞鐵，機場之類。<br />\n<br />\n你可以用依個大型活動，希望部份有心人罷工去響應［大型不合作運動］，而唔係將活動定性為［三罷］。原因就上面有講<br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕不認同，繼續使用三罷名義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論"},{"pid":"9ddd7cc86896d1d5dabec09371ab94c5feeca9c6","tid":1700210,"uid":94771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"時實罷工組織成立當中，而唔係處於０的狀態"},{"pid":"9da022d73a3c78fb85bccfffbc45b14777a58e92","tid":1700210,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"你好勤力出行動post<br />\n巴打好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34720184b3b9d5652a674870d497dd3e6046d2f6","tid":1700210,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52068c78a44226cd81f907fa1b84c351f0d1729","tid":1700210,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d25091efcd6c303d55b733574f85302f5ebb8e4","tid":1700210,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20