thread/1696517/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n罷工group唔夠人呀，大家即刻入group討論啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=554b1fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n公海 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0313e24e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a><br />\n罷工相關常見問題 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F86&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=a78bd79a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/86</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=70fbbcf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=2f746c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a>"},{"pid":"b4c99d2465d3cfcc3e6cfb6c0bc35d910a3cdad2","tid":1700210,"uid":1068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"Why not both ? 人人有責"},{"pid":"a9461643c853525000334145698fc7e04c396a21","tid":1700210,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n大罷工仲要時間籌備"},{"pid":"d2a8baf59007fca4df40e25135a4c2212785937c","tid":1700210,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:39